{
  "stem": "12337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So we were more fearful of the [NON-ENGLISH] than of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "At least, you get a bullet, and it's all over with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every time we would get ready to leave, he would look at me, and he would cry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very kind-- a very religious person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, what did this child do to deserve?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- and so start making-- he would-- he would make excuses, and he would say, oh, it's so cold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's snowing, or this, or that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's do it tomorrow, and tomorrow never came, 'cause he-- What, Pavlo was making excuses or your father?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Pavlo.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father couldn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, Pavlo was making excuses for himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he just-- he knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was so many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were so many times that the Germans and the Ukrainians would come on the farm looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and on his farm, he had a brother on the same farm that never knew that we existed, that he would have given us away in a minute.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was just his children and his wife knew that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is how we-- we spend 18 months-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
